### ğŸ§  Summary:

| Role                  | How often used? | Why?                               |
| --------------------- | --------------- | ---------------------------------- |
| **DevOps Engineer**   | Very often âœ…    | For flexible and automated scripts |
| **Backend Developer** | Sometimes âœ…     | For helper or CLI tools            |

So learning command line arguments is **very helpful** for both paths â€” and **essential** if you're aiming to master automation and flexible scripting ğŸ’¡.


